text: Imay-Utarovo () is a rural locality (a selo) in Moskovsky Selsoviet, Dyurtyulinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 325 as of 2010. There are 7 streets. == Geography == It is located 19 km from Dyurtyuli, 6 km from Moskovo. == References == Category:Rural localities in Dyurtyulinsky District
title: Imay-Utarovo
